item.title: Probably Chests Mod
item.description: This mod adds pots and chests that spawn all over the world, but beware as some chests are more than meets the eye. 8,000 + Downloads About Development Probably Chests is a minecraft mod made for the fabric loader. It is my third Minecraft mod; created in April of 2022. Creating this mod was a new challenge as I got to learn how to use the GeckoLib library to create interesting animations for the mimics.
